You find yourself in a shed. A standard one. The room seems oddly familiar, as though it were only superficially different from the other rooms in the building.

You scan the room, seeing a toolbox. The toolbox is empty, what a horrible day! You can make out a workbench. The workbench is wooden. Looks like someone's already been here and taken everything off it, though.

There is an open wooden door leading west.
